{"tid":1141751,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"試食幅射小火龍蛋糕","createTime":"2019-05-06T16:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T09:10:13.000Z","uid":235546,"like":710,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"23fb4b6719dcba9bdba3985f7495525d17da69c1","tid":1141751,"uid":235546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:25:17.000Z","msg":"話說，前日就見到個post<br />\n<br />\n東海堂出輻射小火龍蛋糕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1138308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1138308</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n咁見到隻小火龍啱啱剝完智慧齒咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就即刻喺第二日狗衝去買嚟試吓味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買返嚟係咁嘅樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oaAV01i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoaAV01i.png&h=84df8503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實個外觀比起張廣告圖，都唔算真係太差嘅<br />\n至少冇太過牙肉腫，但都係似中咗幅射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食咗佢對腳，味道冇咩特別，算係個普通蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再食埋個心口嚿朱古力，點知難食到仆街<br />\n呢世仔都未食過咁難食嘅朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完呢到少少，就擺返咗入雪櫃，打算今日再食<br />\n<br />\n我自己一向腸胃唔好<br />\n放完入雪櫃就開始嚟料<br />\n我個肚起勢咁痛啦，又肚吓痾咁<br />\n痾到屎忽窿都爆埋，慘過俾個黑人雞姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起初我以為朝早食錯嘢<br />\n但今日再食埋個小火龍，食到佢剩返個頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHoXuWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHoXuWS.png&h=9b3ec901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢啲朱古力依然係好撚難食啦<br />\n咁我食完，我屌，又肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我而家初步懷疑有隻小火龍喺我肚入面燒緊我個肚<br />\n如果下次出比卡超蛋糕係咪會直接搞出人命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80170fe34526236f884054f2f4d530c383b1d62","tid":1141751,"uid":62822,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:27:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"797205056b7654eeba760a748d30f024098a121e","tid":1141751,"uid":235546,"like":582,"dislike":8,"score":574,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:27:34.000Z","msg":"我屌，真係有比卡超蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q6wuk5n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq6wuk5n.png&h=afb8825e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe7b49c0f74f77b59fad8ad6228c1c116ac770fc","tid":1141751,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:27:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3658ceae980364e7801c8f5977bbf4fbba6784d4","tid":1141751,"uid":62822,"like":38,"dislike":9,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:27:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32e1244354bf8b396149afc42fbfefa6eb032165","tid":1141751,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:28:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ff9b40c761e4f79a9fbc35e09552c8de5243bd2","tid":1141751,"uid":38737,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:28:33.000Z","msg":"出完比卡超先出小火龍架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7e85c751ec798d3ebfd1b4e9604c010880f41a","tid":1141751,"uid":235546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f80170fe34526236f884054f2f4d530c383b1d62","tid":1141751,"uid":62822,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:27:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:28:41.000Z","msg":"朱古力嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f842ed1abb97524b2fd85c45e246ecd0dda2626f","tid":1141751,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f5aa4d3926498b13ecb99908c486d7d621f026e","tid":1141751,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"